org.netbeans.spi.java.project.support.ui.templates

Interface JavaFileWizardIteratorFactory


  • public interface JavaFileWizardIteratorFactory
    Allows to extend the New Java File Wizard by project specific panels. The instance of the JavaFileWizardIteratorFactory placed in the project's Lookup is consulted by the New Java File Wizard for additional panels.
    Since:
    1.69

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      WizardDescriptor.Iterator<WizardDescriptor> createIterator(FileObject template)
      Creates an WizardDescriptor.Iterator with project specific panels for given template.

    • Method Detail

      • createIterator

        @CheckForNull
WizardDescriptor.Iterator<WizardDescriptor> createIterator(@NonNull
                                                                         FileObject template)
        Creates an WizardDescriptor.Iterator with project specific panels for given template. When the created WizardDescriptor.Iterator is an instance of the WizardDescriptor.InstantiatingIterator the WizardDescriptor.InstantiatingIterator life cycle methods such as WizardDescriptor.InstantiatingIterator#instantiate are called on proper places.
        Parameters:
        template - the template to create additional panels for
        Returns:
        the WizardDescriptor.Iterator with additional panels or null when no additional panels.
